01:09:24,675 --> 01:09:26,905
I'm not your father's neighbour.

450
01:09:29,847 --> 01:09:31,109
I love you.

451
01:09:33,884 --> 01:09:35,977
Frogmen are quick.

452
01:09:36,487 --> 01:09:39,615
A frogman has to make
very quick decisions.

453
01:09:41,392 --> 01:09:42,620
I love you.

454
01:09:47,932 --> 01:09:49,456
You don't know me.

455
01:09:50,501 --> 01:09:52,332
I know you a lot.

456
01:09:54,305 --> 01:09:56,569
And what I know, I find beautiful.

457
