469
01:15:20,931 --> 01:15:23,024
You love her, she wants to die.

470
01:15:23,267 --> 01:15:25,929
Sounds compatible.
Marry her and keep quiet...

471
01:15:26,570 --> 01:15:28,333
especially in a bar.

472
01:15:30,874 --> 01:15:32,466
Thanks for the drink.

473
01:15:33,076 --> 01:15:34,236
Good night.

474
01:15:37,814 --> 01:15:38,940
Thanks.

475
01:16:23,327 --> 01:16:26,319
It's all the same in the end, dad...

476
01:16:31,001 --> 01:16:32,559
It's all the same.

